        "cooked": "<p><a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/collapsible-sidebar-hide-left-contact-drawer-to-show-only-avatars/6372\">Hiding the left sidebar</a> is useful to:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>hide the details (last message) of any chats you may have</li>\n<li>provide more focus and screen real estate for the currently open chat</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Itâ€™s great that this is possible since late 2021 (<a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/2454#issuecomment-984947432\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Responsive collapsable gutter (side menu) Â· Issue #2454 Â· signalapp/Signal-Desktop Â· GitHub</a>).</p>\n<p><strong>It would be even nicer if a shortcut were available for this action,</strong> since itâ€™s one I perform often. The current method, dragging, gets tedious.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/blob/1898e964adcfc8a9096b4aaebff895813fb4f35c/ts/components/NavSidebar.tsx#L105-L1307\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">From the code</a> I figured out that the drag handlebar can already be selected by using the Tab key and then collapsed/shown using left/right left/right keys. Still, a single shortcut for this same action would make it easier and more efficient.</p>\n<p><strong>Ideas for possible shortcuts</strong> (seen from macOS)</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Cmd + .</code>: used by Figma for hiding/showing all sidebars, as of yet unassigned (I think)</li>\n<li><code>Cmd + \\</code>:\n<details>\n<summary>\ncourtesy of a ChatGPT hallucination</summary>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/3/4/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c\" title=\"CleanShot 2024-08-30 at 16.19.39@2x\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/4/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c_2_690x373.png\" alt=\"CleanShot 2024-08-30 at 16.19.39@2x\" data-base62-sha1=\"7w8TXOsNjT6c0DQt7nP5gyTfYRK\" width=\"690\" height=\"373\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/4/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c_2_690x373.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/4/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c_2_1035x559.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/3/4/34b165f9b53eefa7813d9ffd79d0973bd11d182c_2_1380x746.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"F8F8F8\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">CleanShot 2024-08-30 at 16.19.39@2x</span><span class=\"informations\">1812Ã—982 45.8 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n</details>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>References</strong><br>\nSome people whoâ€™ve brought this feature request up before, in comments on GitHub:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/1845#issuecomment-2002365335\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">feature requests: clear screen; hide contact list Â· Issue #1845 Â· signalapp/Signal-Desktop Â· GitHub</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/signalapp/Signal-Desktop/issues/2454#issuecomment-926560999\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Responsive collapsable gutter (side menu) Â· Issue #2454 Â· signalapp/Signal-Desktop Â· GitHub</a></li>\n</ul>",
